Live masterclasses by Texas McCombs’ faculty: Learn directly from top, world renowned faculty at McCombs School of Business, who bring cutting-edge industry insights and research-backed methodologies.

Weekly live mentorship sessions: Connect with industry mentors who provide project guidance and share best practices.

Practical, hands-on learning: Work on industry-relevant projects and explore real-world case studies, applying AI techniques to solve business challenges in marketing, finance, operations, and customer experience.

Extensive curriculum: Gain hands-on expertise in deep learning, embeddings, transformers, LLMs, retrieval-augmented generation (RAG), and Agentic AI workflows—all within a structured, business-focused learning environment.

Peer learning & global networking: Collaborate with professionals from diverse industries, engage in thought-provoking discussions, and expand your network in the AI space.

Dedicated Program Manager: Get personalized assistance from a dedicated Program Manager, and non-academic support throughout your journey.

Texas McCombs’ Advantage: Earn a prestigious Certificate of Completion and 2.5 Continuing Education Units (CEUs) from Texas McCombs, strengthening your professional profile and opening doors to new career opportunities.
